laboratory_examinations.findings: Non-union of a fracture of the proximal epiphysis of the middle phalanx.
Sclerosis of a dorsal epiphyseal fragment still attached to the growth plate, without any sign of displacement or consolidation.
Exclusion of pulley rupture, no abnormal findings in the extensor or flexor tendons, showed a high signal between the two epiphyseal fragments on T2-weighted sequences.
